OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779451870
OL,3,CTwo children and woman critically
OL,4,Cinjured after 'horrendous' crash
OL,6,FTwo young children and a woman are
OL,7,Fcritically injured in hospital after a
OL,8,F"horrendous" crash involving two cars.
OL,10,FThe A59 was closed for several hours
OL,11,Fas a huge emergency services responded
OL,12,Fto the crash involving a Skoda and VW
OL,13,FGolf, which happened the village of
OL,14,FGisburn, Lancashire, just before 4pm
OL,15,Fon Thursday, 21 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
