PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779451870
OL,3,CTwo children and woman critically
OL,4,Cinjured after 'horrendous' crash
OL,6,FThe driver of the Skoda, a woman in
OL,7,Fher 60s, and two passengers ` a boy
OL,8,Fand a girl both aged five ` all
OL,9,Fsuffered severe injuries and were
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital where they are in a
OL,11,Fcritical condition, police said.
OL,13,FA man in his 20s, who was the driver
OL,14,Fin the other car, was taken to
OL,15,Fhospital with serious injuries.
OL,17,FLancashire Police have launched a full
OL,18,Finvestigation into the circumstances
OL,19,Fsurrounding the crash and are urgently
OL,20,Fappealing to the public for
OL,21,Finformation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
