PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779451870
OL,3,CTwo children and woman critically
OL,4,Cinjured after 'horrendous' crash
OL,6,FIn a statement, Sergeant Anthony
OL,7,FBeckett said: "This was an horrendous
OL,8,Fcollision involving two cars and
OL,9,Finvolved a huge response from the
OL,10,Femergency services.
OL,12,F"As we investigate the collision, we
OL,13,Fare appealing for any witnesses to
OL,14,Fcome forward and for anyone who has
OL,15,Fdashcam footage to contact us."
